  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The main objective of this trial is to evaluate endoscopic visualization during a
      laparoscopic sleeve gastrectomy (LSG) procedure using an endoscope inserted transvaginally
      through a new device called a Steerable Flex Trocar (SFT).
    </textblock>
